headline.print_headline: Car Bomb Kills 15 People in Central Baghdad: Police
headline.main: Car Bomb Kills 15 People in Central Baghdad: Police

lead_paragraph: A car bomb killed at least 15 people in central Baghdad on Monday, police and medical sources in the Iraqi capital said.
